## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="96baa-102">Aparaty synteza mowy niestandardowej zdefiniować typy zdarzeń przesłanych w infrastrukturze syntezatora mowy platformy za pomocą <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="96baa-102">Custom speech synthesis engines define the types of events submitted to the Speech platform synthesizer infrastructure with the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="96baa-103">Specyfikacja odbywa się przez ustawienie <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo.EventId%2A> właściwość <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> wystąpienia przekazane do <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.AddEvents%2A> członek klasy wykonania <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> interfejsu przekazany do <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A> metody aparatu rozpoznawania mowy niestandardowej Implementacja <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="96baa-103">Specification is performed by setting the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo.EventId%2A> property of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> instances passed to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.AddEvents%2A> member of the class implementing the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> interface passed to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A> method on a custom speech engine's implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="96baa-104">Infrastruktury platformy mowy wskazuje typ zdarzenia, które obecnie obsługuje za pośrednictwem <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> właściwość <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> przekazany do implementacji Mów.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="96baa-104">The Speech platform infrastructure indicates the type of events it is currently handling through the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> passed to the speak implementation.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="96baa-105">Wartość <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> jest, gdzie członkowie <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId> Zdefiniuj lokalizację bitowe odpowiadające typu zdarzenia.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="96baa-105">The value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> is a bitmask, where the members of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId> define the location of the bit corresponding to the event type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="96baa-106">Na przykład WordBoundary wynosi pięć (5), co oznacza piąty bitu w wartości zwracanej przez <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> wskazuje, czy witryna obsługuje typ zdarzenia.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="96baa-106">For example, WordBoundary has a value of five (5), meaning the fifth bit in the value returned by <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> indicates if the site supports the event type.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="96baa-107">W poniższym przykładzie przedstawiono część wykonania synteza mowy niestandardowej, dziedziczenie z <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>i przy użyciu programu <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>, i <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="96baa-107">The example below is part of a custom speech synthesis implementation inheriting from <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>, and using the use of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>, and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="96baa-108">Implementacja <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="96baa-108">The implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span></span>  
  
1.  <span data-ttu-id="96baa-109">Odbiera tablicę <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> wystąpień i tworzy nową tablicę z <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> wystąpień, które zostaną przekazane do `Speak` metody na aparacie syntezy podstawowej.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="96baa-109">Receives an array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances and creates a new array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances to be passed to the `Speak` method on an underlying synthesis engine.</span></span>  
  
2.  <span data-ttu-id="96baa-110">Jeśli <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction> wartość wyliczenia przez znaleźć <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> właściwość <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> zwrócone przez <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> właściwości każdego <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> wystąpienie jest <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction>, wykonania</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="96baa-110">If the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction> enumeration value by found from the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> returned by the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> property of each <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> instance is <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction>, the implementation</span></span>  
  
    -   <span data-ttu-id="96baa-111">Tłumaczy Americanism do Britishisms w tekst, który ma być używany.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="96baa-111">Translates Americanism to Britishisms in the text to be spoken.</span></span>  
  
    -   <span data-ttu-id="96baa-112">Jeśli <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> właściwość <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> zapewniane dla implementacji interfejsów obsługuje WordBoundary typu zdarzenia, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> wystąpienia jest używany do tworzenia zdarzenia wskaźnik postępu Syntezator jest tworzony dysk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="96baa-112">If the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> interfaces provided to the implementation support the WordBoundary event type, a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> instance is used to create an event to drive a synthesizer progress meter is created.</span></span>  
  
3.  <span data-ttu-id="96baa-113">Aparat renderowania mowy jest następnie wywoływana za pomocą zmodyfikowanego <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> tablicy.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="96baa-113">A speech rendering engine is then called with the modified <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> array.</span></span>  
  
```  
private const int WordBoundaryFlag = 1 << (int)TtsEventId.WordBoundary;  
private readonly char[] spaces = new char[] { ' ', '\t', '\r', '\n' };  
internal struct UsVsUk  
{  
  internal string UK;  
  internal string US;  
}  
  
override public void Speak (TextFragment [] frags, IntPtr wfx, ITtsEngineSite site)  
{  
  TextFragment [] newFrags=new TextFragment[frags.Length];  
  
  for (int i=0;i<frags.Length;i++){  
    newFrags[i].State=frags[i].State;  
    //truncate  
    newFrags[i].TextToSpeak = frags[i].TextToSpeak.Substring(frags[i].TextOffset,  
                               frags[i].TextLength);  
    newFrags[i].TextLength = newFrags[i].TextToSpeak.Length;  
    newFrags[i].TextOffset = 0;  
    if (newFrags[i].State.Action == TtsEngineAction.Speak) {  
      //Us to UK conversion  
      foreach (UsVsUk term in TransList) {  
      newFrags[i].TextToSpeak.Replace(term.US, term.UK);  
      }  
      //Generate progress meter events if supported  
      if ((site.EventInterest & WordBoundaryFlag) != 0) {  
      string[] subs = newFrags[i].TextToSpeak.Split(spaces);  
  
      foreach (string s in subs) {  
        int offset = newFrags[i].TextOffset;  
        SpeechEventInfo spEvent = new SpeechEventInfo((Int16)TtsEventId.WordBoundary,   
                (Int16)EventParameterType.Undefined,   
                 s.Length, new IntPtr(offset));  
        offset += s.Length;  
        if (s.Trim().Length > 0) {  
          SpeechEventInfo[] events = new SpeechEventInfo[1];  
          events[0] = spEvent;  
          site.AddEvents(events, 1);  
        }  
      }  
      }  
    }  
  }  
  
  _baseSynthesize.Speak(newFrags, wfx, site);  
  
}  
```
